export default function AppHeader() {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar className="bg-body-tertiary" expand="lg">
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Brand href="#home">WANDERLOGIXS</Navbar.Brand>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                        <Nav className="justify-content-center w-100 custom-nav-spacing">
                            <Nav.Link href="#home">Dashboard</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Trips</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Expenses</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Itinerary</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Media</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link" style={{ marginRight: '40px' }}>Itinerary</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                        <Form className="d-flex">
                            <Form.Control
                                type="search"
                                placeholder="Search"
                                className="me-2"
                                aria-label="Search"
                            />
                            <Button type="submit">Submit</Button>
                        </Form>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </>
    );
}
